</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Attn Sports Editors: &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for Monday,
Jan. 11:
</P>
<P>
   FBN-JETS-JAGUARS (East Rutherford, N.J.) _ The Jets beat
Jacksonville 34-24 to advance to the AFC finals against Denver on
Sunday. By Gerald Eskenazi.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-JETS-KEYSHAWN (East Rutherford, N.J.) _ Column on Jets
receiver Keyshawn Johnson, who had 121 yards receiving, 28 yards
rushing, scored two touchdowns and even intercepted a pass on
