u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AMAZON-STOCK-ADVISORY     01-10 0036
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AMAZON-STOCK-ADVISORY-NYT </SLUG>
  
(sw) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORIS/GRAPHICS EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   Eds: The story AMAZON-STOCK will not have a graphic as
previously indicated in a refiling.
</P>
</TEXT>
