   The Kansas City Royals wanted to hire Northridge's Mark Gubicza
back as a minor-league pitching instructor. Gubicza, 36, who tried
out recently for the Boston Red Sox, wants back in the Royals'
rotation....
</P>
<P>
   A yarn going around the Fox offices: When Rupert Murdoch was
asked for his approval of the $105 million contract for pitcher
